title: Mapping Notation
text: Each arrow matches the person to their birthday.

title: Creating Ordered Pairs
text: We create ordered pairs with the person’s name as the x-value and their birthday as the y-value. We get {(Alison, April 25), (Penelope, May 23), (June, August 2), (Gregory, September 15), (Geoffrey, January 12), (Lauren, May 10), (Stephen, July 24), (Alice, February 3), (Liz, August 2), (Danny, July 24)}
